highlights.text: “Robarte un Beso” by Carlos Vives and Sebastian Yatra is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 56 spots at #90.
Ed Sheeran has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Shape of You” is the highest at #8.
“That's What I Like” by Bruno Mars has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 34 weeks straight.
“Without You (feat. Sandro Cavazza)” by Avicii and Sandro Cavazza is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #26.
